      "rationale": "A single mesh density of 2.1 million polyhedral cells was used for all production simulations. No formal Richardson extrapolation or GCI calculation was performed. A qualitative visual inspection of velocity contours on coarse versus fine mesh was considered sufficient by the assessment team, yielding an informal estimate of mesh independence. This does not satisfy the Gradation 3 requirement for quantified discretization uncertainty."
