    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 V&V 40 factors. Seven factors were formally assessed and determined to meet or exceed required gradation levels. Six factors were not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The team concluded that the CFD model provides High assurance for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the stated COU. The discretization error factor was judged adequate based on qualitative mesh sensitivity review. Overall assurance level declared High.",
